      "reason": "When PaymentService fails after OrderService succeeds, the order and inventory reservation are orphaned with no rollback mechanism. This is a data consistency bug that will manifest on every payment failure — not an edge case. The integration architecture requires a compensation pattern (saga, event-driven rollback, or synchronous undo) before it can ship.",
